    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Round or oval sand-filled leather cushions used as a base when engraving silverware or stamps. An engraving block or an engraving board is placed on this, making it lie firmly but still easy to turn.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
